WEBVTT

00:03.239 --> 00:05.140
You would have us march
to our end?

00:05.208 --> 00:06.608
I would have us free.

00:06.676 --> 00:08.777
With or without you

00:08.845 --> 00:11.548
I shall march upon Rome.

00:11.615 --> 00:14.083
You were slave
to Marcus Crassus himself?

00:14.151 --> 00:15.285
I was.

00:15.352 --> 00:16.786
Why would she risk all

00:16.854 --> 00:18.656
to fly from loving arms?

00:20.324 --> 00:21.892
Tomorrow we move
for Rome with Crixus.

00:21.959 --> 00:23.627
Yet I would have
you take with Spartacus.

00:23.694 --> 00:25.362
My place is forever with you.

00:25.429 --> 00:27.330
Not in this.

00:27.398 --> 00:29.278
The whore Canthara tells
of how she saw you come

00:29.334 --> 00:30.701
from Kore's tent.

00:30.768 --> 00:32.067
Game is over boy.

00:35.706 --> 00:37.172
Take it like a woman.

00:37.240 --> 00:40.309
Rome at last
lies within our grasp!

